{"tid":1616060,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTVB 報道 明召開行會立蒙面緊急法","createTime":"2019-10-03T09:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T09:53:38.000Z","uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"18d85da85b484ab8bb781bdd4eeeeffd29635160","tid":1616060,"uid":293951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:32:55.000Z","msg":"CCTVB 報道 明召開行會立蒙面緊急法， 林鄭月娥之前又提出取消今年區議會選舉。 呢個香港已經無晒人權可言。日日都搞咁多新野出嚟。我聽過一句說話對住中國人你唔向佢哋推前一步, 佢就會逼你退後兩步。所以絕對要逼迫佢哋，唔可以比佢哋有反彈嘅空間。 正如民建聯一樣，一有空間就搞事。幾時有人可以去掟個汽油彈入禮賓府，等林鄭月娥同班民建聯唔好得寸進尺。"},{"pid":"c2aa4efe9eefc0f9ce01ae0fb572a2c3ae863a2e","tid":1616060,"uid":3893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T09:53:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/K1g8kdJBeAw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FK1g8kdJBeAw&d=Sqlr%2BNOTUp1GXDSzM%2FaCEtRt30ToQ9uN2xIpFOlVN1U%3D&h=a6d51740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/K1g8kdJBeAw</a>"}]}